y" pp. 286–295, 291, in ''General History of Africa, volume II. Ancient Civilizations of Africa'' (UNESCO 1990), Abridged Edition.</ref><ref>C.B.M.McBurney, ''The Stone Age of Northern Africa'' (Pelican 1960) pp. 258–266.</ref>

